yn y october   poison gas may carry a medical benefit the boston globe retrieved october     gilliam o r johnson c m gordy w  microwave spectroscopy in the region from two to three millimeters physical review   – bibcodephrvg doiphysrev   haynes william m  handbook of chemistry and physics  ed boca raton florida crc press p – isbn    haynes william m  handbook of chemistry and physics  ed boca raton florida crc press p – isbn    common bond energies d and bond lengths r wiredchemistcom  vidal c r  june  highly excited triplet states of carbon monoxide archived from the original on  retrieved august     scuseria gustavo e miller michael d jensen frank geertsen jan  the dipole moment of carbon monoxide j chem phys    bibcodejchphs doi   lupinetti anthony j fau stefan frenking gernot strauss steven h  theoretical analysis of the bonding between co and positively charged atoms j phys chem a   – doijpl   blanco fernando alkorta ibon solimannejad mohammad elguero jose  theoretical study of the  complexes between carbon monoxide and hypohalous acids j phys chem a   – pmid  doijph   meerts w de leeuw fh dymanus a  june  electric and magnetic properties of carbon monoxide by molecularbeam electricresonance spectroscopy chemical physics   – bibcodecpm doix   stefan thorsten janoschek rudolf  how relevant are so and po double bonds for the description of the acid molecules hso hso and hpo respectively journal of molecular modeling   – doipl   omaye st  metabolic modulation of carbon monoxide toxicity toxicology   – pmid  doisx   tikuisis p kane dm mclellan tm buick f fairburn sm  rate of formation of carboxyhemoglobin in exercising humans exposed to carbon monoxide journal of applied physiology   – pmid    osha co guidelines osha archived from the original on january   retrieved may   check date values in accessdate help  a b blumenthal ivan  june  carbon monoxide poisoning j r soc med the royal society of medicine   – pmc   pmid    ganong william f   review of medical physiol