 is provided by manufacturers suppliers and others and has not been verified by us see our disclaimer the acdc kidde carbon monoxide and gas alarm provides you with protection during emergency situations and power outages it shows the level of carbon monoxide present in the air and helps you prepare for an evacuation if needed the carbon monoxide gas detector can be placed in any ac outlet the gas sensor in the alarm also detects levels of methane and propane in the air at the simple touch of a button the digital display is easy to read and shows the exact recorded levels of carbon monoxide the explosive gas alarm can be used in most any business or residential space easily you just plug it in and it is ready to start protecting you from buildups of invisible gases the unit has a memory that can recall the highest levels of gases recorded helping ensure your constant safety kidde carbon monoxide and gas alarm digitally displays the level of carbon monoxide the unit is sensing testreset button tests the unit for proper operation and resets the alarm peak level memory recalls the highest co concentration detected nighthawk alarm is easy to use and set up in the home or office simply read the screen to find out the levels of different gases inside the building specificationsconditionnewmanufacturer part numbermodelbrandkiddeshow moremanuals  guidescarbon monoxide faqspdf    pagesviewhow to choose a carbon monoxide alarmpdf    pagesviewgo to previous slide  of go to next slide  of carousel page  of  activecarousel page  of  falsevideosvideo is not supported in this browserplay againdoes my home need carbon monoxide alarmsquestions  answers questionsget specific details about this product from customers who own itbackask a questionquestions  answershave a question find answers here or ask a question of your ownsort by number of answersmost recent questionsmost recent answers of  questionsbackwhat else detects beside cocan you please let me know what else detects beside c